  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Cristal Lodge is an eclectic Alpine hotel with a central location in <span>Chantemerle, one of the main districts of Serre Chevalier. The hotel benefits from being a short walk away from the ski lifts and resort centre, where you can find a range of shops, bars and restaurants. After a day of adventures, head back to the hotel for a drink or two at the tapas bar, or unwind in the wellness area.</span><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Cosy and comfortable</span></h2>
<p><span>The hotel has a modern feel to it, with eclectic touches including disco balls and a phone box adorning the lobby and reception area. The rooms are furnished in a simplistic Alpine design, and provide a comfortable place to stay in a great location. </span><span>If you want a bit more privacy, the Residence Cristal Lodge, offers spacious and modern self catering apartments as well.</span></p>
<h2><span>Unwind and relax</span></h2>
<p><span>After a day of exploring the slopes of <a data-udi="umb://document/b7e31f4645514434bec76a3728e974c0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b7e31f4645514434bec76a3728e974c0}" title="Serre Chevalier">Serre Chevalier</a>, make the most of the wellness facilities included with your stay. Soothe any aches and pains in the jacuzzi, or unwind in the sauna and hammam. Treat yourself to a massage or spa treatment for a moment of pure relaxation. </span></p>
<h2><span>Bar and lounge </span></h2>
<p><span>The lounge area is a great spot to chill after a day of skiing or snowboarding, sample some Savoyard style tapas or enjoy live music once a week with a glass of wine. There's a big foosball table to get competitive on, and a playroom to keep the kids occupied. </span></p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
